Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:57.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雙腿的腳步聲  傳向遙遠的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:01.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}宣告願託付一切的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:07.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}飛向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:25.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}擦身而過的敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:29.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}從迷惑中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:33.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}若要前往奔赴啟程的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:37.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}便不會放開這雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:40.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}初次相互凝視的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:44.27,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}至今依然記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:47.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}即使被微眠的漩渦所吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:54.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}我們的見證也不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:59.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}輕撫臉頰的手心  微笑著的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:02.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}我願將其守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:06.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}雖然繞了遠路  但我還是發現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}我一直只為了你而活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:13.30,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}在光之雪花飛舞的夜空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:16.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}殘月孤星互相依偎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.10,0:23:20.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}我們曾編織的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:24.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fs20\an3}今後也永遠不會結束
